content: The forms uploaded by the administrators will be appeared here.

comment.text: This translation key is used for a placeholder text that will be displayed on an empty form folder, indicating its purpose. It's likely to appear in a UI component where a list or view of files is expected but none are present.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The English phrase 'will be appeared' is grammatically incorrect. The correct phrasing would be 'will appear'. The Arabic translation doesn't reflect this and could be improved to be more natural.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: ستظهر هنا النماذج التي قام المسؤولون بتحميلها.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'Administratorlar tərəfindən yüklənmiş formalar burada görünəcək' is a literal translation and doesn't quite capture the intended meaning of 'will be appeared'. A more natural phrasing in Azerbaijani would be something like 'Administratorlar tərəfindən yüklənmiş formalar burada göstəriləcək' or 'Administratorlar tərəfindən yüklənmiş formaları burada görə bilərsiniz'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Administratorlar tərəfindən yüklənmiş formaları burada görə bilərsiniz.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'Zde se objeví formuláře nahrané správci' is technically correct, but lacks the nuance of the original English. 'Will be appeared' is a somewhat awkward phrasing. A more natural translation would convey that the forms *will appear* or *are displayed* here.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Zde se zobrazí formuláře nahrané správci.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The English content 'The forms uploaded by the administrators will be appeared here' implies the forms *will* appear. The Finnish translation 'Pääkäyttäjien lataamat lomakkeet ilmestyvät tänne' translates to 'The forms uploaded by the administrators will appear here.' While technically correct, it lacks the present tense feel of what a user would expect to see. A more natural translation would emphasize the forms are currently visible.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Pääkäyttäjien lataamat lomakkeet ovat nähtävissä täällä.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'Ադմինիստրատորների կողմից վերբեռնված ձևերը կհայտնվեն այստեղ:' is a literal translation and doesn't convey the intended meaning as smoothly as it could. A more natural phrasing would be preferred.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Ադմինիստրատորները վերբեռնած ձևերը տեղադրվելու են այստեղ:

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Lao translation doesn't fully convey the meaning of the English sentence. "ຈະປະກົດຢູ່ທີ່ນີ້" literally means 'will appear here', but the English implies a default or standard location. A better translation would indicate that these forms are *typically* or *usually* found here.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: ແບບຟອມທີ່ບັນຊາກອນອັບໂຫຼດໄວ້ ຈະປະກົດຢູ່ທີ່ນີ້ ຕາມປົກກະຕິ (Bap form thi banchakorn up load vai ja prakot yu thi ni tam pokkati)

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Romanian translation uses the incorrect verb form 'vor fi' (will be). It should be 'vor apărea' (will appear) to better match the English phrasing and meaning. 'Vor fi afișate' is grammatically correct, but less natural in this context.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Formularele încărcate de administratorul vor apărea aici.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'පරිපාලකවරු විසින් උඩුගත කරන ලද ආකෘතීන් මෙහි දිස්වනු ඇත' while generally conveying the meaning, isn't the most natural or accurate translation of 'The forms uploaded by the administrators will be appeared here.' A more natural phrasing would emphasize 'will be displayed' rather than 'will appear'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: පරිපාලකවරු විසින් උඩුගත කරන ලද ආකෘතීන් මෙහි පෙන්විලි කරනු ඇත.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The English phrasing 'will be appeared' is grammatically incorrect. The translation, while conveying the meaning, doesn't directly reflect this error. A more accurate reflection of the original's awkwardness, or a more natural translation would be preferable.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Forms uploaded by administrators will be displayed here.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'ће се појавити овде' is a bit literal and less natural in Serbian. A more natural phrasing would be something along the lines of 'појавиће се овде' or 'налазиће се овде'.
The word 'otpremljeni' is a less common and slightly awkward way to say 'uploaded' in this context. A more natural translation would be 'ugovoreni' or 'uneseni'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Formulari ugovoreni od strane administratora će se pojaviti ovde.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase 'će se pojaviti ovde' is grammatically correct but sounds a bit clunky. A more fluent phrasing would be 'prikazaće se ovde' or 'biće prikazani ovde'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Formulari ugovoreni od strane administratora biće prikazani ovde.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'Тут з'являться форми, передані адміністраторами' doesn't fully convey the meaning of 'will be appeared'. It implies 'will appear' which is a subtle but important difference.  'Transferred' ('передані') also doesn't quite capture the meaning of 'uploaded'.
